# ============ Warframe Metadata Editor — .gitignore ============

# --- .NET build output / intermediates ---
**/bin/
**/obj/
editor/build/
*.user
.vs/

# --- Standalone build artifacts (regenerated by `dotnet publish`; see Build/README.txt) ---
Build/*.exe
Build/*.dll

# --- Proprietary Oodle decompressor (RAD Game Tools / Epic — DO NOT redistribute) ---
**/oo2core*.dll
editor/lib/

# --- Game-derived data & cache (large; not for redistribution) ---
data/
**/*.dec
**/*.cache
**/*.toc
**/Packages.bin*
**/Languages.bin*
**/*.jsonl

# --- Third-party reference source (upstreams noted in EDITOR_NOTES.md §7) ---
reference/

# --- Exploratory RE history (hundreds of scratch scripts w/ machine-specific paths) ---
decoder/_re_history/

# --- Large generated decoder outputs (game-derived; regenerated by the decoder scripts) ---
decoder/rec_paths.txt
decoder/*.json
**/*.tsv
decoder/*_decoded_*.txt
decoder/grnbow_decoded_own.txt

# --- Python cache ---
**/__pycache__/
*.pyc

